cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use CircuitRubric, please cite it."
title: "CircuitRubric: A Structural Benchmark for LLM-Generated Analog Netlists"
abstract: >-
  A 125-fixture benchmark and graph-isomorphism grader with a 6-level partial-credit
  ladder for evaluating the structural correctness of LLM-generated analog circuit
  netlists, without SPICE simulation.
authors:
  - family-names: "El-Chammas"
    given-names: "Manar"
type: software
repository-code: "https://github.com/levantlabs/circuitrubric-bench"
url: "https://github.com/levantlabs/circuitrubric-bench"
